column2: SELECT    sph.ra, sph.dec,   s.z, s.snMedian_r, s.velDisp,   s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,    sph.fiberMag_g,sph.fiberMagErr_g,sph.extinction_g,   sph.fiberMag_r,sph.fiberMagerr_r,sph.extinction_r,   ge.bptclass, ge.lgm_tot_p5#,   gi.lick_hb,gi.lick_hb_err,   gi.lick_mgb,gi.lick_mgb_err,   gi.lick_fe5#,gi.lick_fe5#_err,   gi.lick_fe5#,gi.lick_fe5#_err,   gi.lick_hd_a,gi.lick_hd_a_err,   gi.d4#_n,gi.d4#_n_err INTO SDSS_SN5_full FROM SpecObj AS s   JOIN galSpecIndx AS gi ON s.specObjID = gi.specObjID   JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON s.specObjID = ge.specObjID   JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sph ON s.specObjID = sph.specObjID WHERE    s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND   s.survey = &&&   AND   s.class = &&&   AND   s.snMedian_r > #   AND   s.zWARNING = #
